        <h3>Tier 1</h3>
        <p>
          Tier 1 decks are the most-played decks in Pioneer. In any tournament of sufficient size you&rsquo;re likely to play against each of these decks, so you should be prepared for them when building decks and sideboards. You should expect the Tier 1 decks to regularly make the Top 8 cut at major tournaments.
        </p>
