        <h3>Tier 2</h3>
        <p>
          Tier 2 decks are strategies that may have tournament viability in Pioneer, but you shouldn&rsquo;t expect to see them in every tournament. An awareness of these decks and their game plan is a good idea, but you can avoid skewing your deck and sideboard to beat them. They can sometimes spike a major tournament to show up in the Top 8, but they won&rsquo;t do so regularly.
